{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843720/extras/PleaseSupportUs_.png?t=1732719140\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Seagulls: Crappy Situation</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An action-packed wave shooter where relaxation isn\u2019t an option! Dive into hilarious bird-hunting, intense multitasking, and strategic micromanagement, all with comedic, rogue-like elements. Your mission? Stay alive while dodging angry birds pooping on your raft!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843720/extras/AnimGifAttack4.gif?t=1732719140\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\ud83d\udea3\u200d Survive on the sea</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take on the role of a lone defender or together with your crew, battling the seagulls that threatens to destroy your raft. Do you have what it takes to survive?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843720/extras/Ready_Set_Aim.gif?t=1732719140\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83c\udfaf<strong>\u00a0Ready, Set, Aim</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Arm yourself with a trusty slingshot and face down wave after wave of airborne attackers! Take precise aim, launch your shots, and watch those feathered foes fall before they can overrun your raft.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843720/extras/AnimGifClean1.gif?t=1732719140\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\ud83d\udebf Clean the raft</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Grab your trusty water hose and brace yourself\u2014the only way to survive is to keep your raft clear of the corrosive guano from relentless seagull bombardments. As the droppings pile up, your raft takes damage, slowly deteriorating under the acidic assault. Scrub it clean or risk watching your raft crumble into the sea!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843720/extras/Test.gif?t=1732719140\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\ud83d\udd28 Build your raft</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Upgrade your defenses to keep pace with the relentless waves of seagulls. Collect resources to reinforce and expand your raft, turning it into a stronger sanctuary amidst the chaos. Every upgrade boosts your chances of survival as the seagull swarms grow fiercer!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843720/extras/AnimGifExplore.gif?t=1732719140\" /> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\ud83e\udd3f Explore the depths</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore a mesmerizing underwater world. Find resources and treasures that will help you to survive and deal with the flying pests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843720/extras/AnimGifUpgrade.gif?t=1732719140\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u26a1\ufe0f\u00a0<strong>Power-up</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Adapt to the changing tides as waves of seagulls are attacking. Upgrade your weapons and raft, buy new items or make them more powerful. Can you defend the raft until help arrives?<strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843720/extras/Wishlist.png?t=1732719140\" />No seagulls was hurt during this production.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam